							<h2 class="major">And then we thought..</h2>

							<p>Using the power of crowed-sourcing, Project Awaaz aspires to extend support to strengthen ‘accessible content’, infrastructure and the right technology so that more and more visually impaired students are able to fulfill their dreams. What they listen to, becomes the world they perceive. Project Awaaz is all about our voices becoming their world. </p>

						</div>

					</div>

				</section>



