							<h2 class="major">This is why it's awesome!</h2>

							<p>With the support of the <a href="http://www.olpv.org">One Library Per Village (OLPV) initiative</a>, Project Awaaz moves ahead of simply recording voices to even delivering content to the people who need them the most. More than just the visually impaired, this project holds the potential to benefit every print-disabled person out there.</p>

